{"tid":174582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"比人係屋企偷咗差唔多成皮嘢","createTime":"2017-03-27T02:14:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-27T03:30:26.000Z","uid":15896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fdb226301926f58d0d49cb2fceeac13f174ca940","tid":174582,"uid":15896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"屋企得我同工人住，工人幫我做左十幾年嘢.<br />\n話說最近去旅行諗住搵番啲外幣睇下有幾多<br />\n點知冇左超過500蚊英磅同埋幾千蚊港紙嘅yen。<br />\n問起工人話佢幾個月前帶左個朋友上嚟, 佢個朋友嚟又問駛唔駛幫手執屋，又摷櫃桶，總之九成九肯定條撚樣偷。<br />\n依家佢係澳門等緊visa嚟香港，佢亦冇再同我工人聯絡，點拎番啲錢好"},{"pid":"78780c7e07d356efef517716fda2f302d8c68883","tid":174582,"uid":55657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"報驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ced6117f36f1fa222b9101e82b3729ba6ed785","tid":174582,"uid":94935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:15:31.000Z","msg":"報驚 你工人做證人"},{"pid":"ce21c2d1c1f2809c966c92164f2b753868da04d6","tid":174582,"uid":34498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:27:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"f51895a99197e1e25ffe5c819b397b28a05dc377","tid":174582,"uid":15896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報驚 你工人做證人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我唔知確實日子，而且又唔知條友確實行蹤<br />\n報驚受理？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b356d31df17ef4b1509aa1c8be484d1d79dbd97","tid":174582,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:36:47.000Z","msg":"根本係你屋企on9，<br />\n冇可能會比工人帶自己朋友上嚟屋企啦係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 由細到大屋企都有工人"},{"pid":"c6bb0416199f217b4fa7754d519fae8cf2069d5c","tid":174582,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:38:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係你屋企on9，<br />\n冇可能會比工人帶自己朋友上嚟屋企啦係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 由細到大屋企都有工人</blockquote><br />\n原來得你同工人住，<br />\n姐係你on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dffce188c6c71019d530696117082aabecb335e7","tid":174582,"uid":84415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T02:40:18.000Z","msg":"樓主有銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f1d9d95da213d5e65f860a4de818c013bffe8","tid":174582,"uid":15896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:08:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主有銀仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就係冇乜銀先想拎番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9522607ab65a3947a206139172d445f8ef4129","tid":174582,"uid":15896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>根本係你屋企on9，<br />\n冇可能會比工人帶自己朋友上嚟屋企啦係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 由細到大屋企都有工人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要番工冇可能會知佢帶人上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2097ac1b4a8fce1a9d8c378052cef2669611106","tid":174582,"uid":52972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"邊有仇報架。 又唔係捉賊拿贓。<br />\n<br />\n報警朋友就推落工人度， 工人又推落朋友度。 就算你話查手指紋（假設隔左咁耐都仲有先算）， 佢又真係有黎過做野喎， 分分鐘仲俾入境處告你僱用非法員工/無第三保險之類， 仲捉蟲。"},{"pid":"11a702516d4ed30b8728c0cd0b31566a5bf2717a","tid":174582,"uid":26003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T03:30:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>根本係你屋企on9，<br />\n冇可能會比工人帶自己朋友上嚟屋企啦係咪呀？<br />\n<br />\n利申: 由細到大屋企都有工人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我要番工冇可能會知佢帶人上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你而家知道就炒撚咗佢啦，<br />\n佢當你冇到先夠膽帶朋友上嚟，<br />\n如果我呀媽知道工人帶啲三唔識七既人上嚟屋企，<br />\n一定即炒"}]}